					<msContents n="1">
						<!--increment n attribute for ms containing multiple ms items-->
						<summary> A 17th-century paper manuscript of <name type="person"
								subtype="aut" key="local_00000 VIAF_">
								<persName xml:lang="sa" type="standard"
								>Bhāvacandrasūri</persName></name>'s <title xml:lang="sa"
								key="local_00000">Śāntināthacaritra</title>. This work describes the
							life of 16th Lord Śāntinātha in Sanskrit prose with his earlier twelve
							births. This is divided into 6 prastāvas (chapters) as below. 1st
							prastāva edns on fol.8B; 2nd ends on fol.20B; 3rd ends on fol.37B; 4th
							ends on fol. 53B; 5th ends on fol.72B; 6th ends on fol.105B </summary>
						<msItem n="1" defective="true">
							<author>
								<name type="person" subtype="aut" key="local_00000 VIAF_">
									<persName xml:lang="sa" type="standard">Bhāvacandrasūri</persName>
								</name>
							</author>
							<title xml:lang="sa" key="local_00000">Śāntināthacaritra</title>
							<rubric xml:lang="sa"><locus from="1v" to="1v">[1v1]</locus> śrī jināya
								namaḥ || </rubric>
							<incipit xml:lang="sa"><locus from="1v" to="1v">[1v1]</locus>
								praṇipatyārtahaḥ sarvān Vāgdevīṃ sadgurun api, gadyabandhena vakṣyāmi
								śrīŚānthi caritaṃ mudā || 1 || sarve saṃsāriṇo jīvā .......[to add from
								fol.34 catl.] kathyante || teṣām ādyā-bhavaḥ procyate || ihe eva
								Jaṃbūdvīpe Bharatakṣetre ananta-ratna-niketanaṃ śrīmad Ratnapuraṃ nāma
								Pattanam asti ...etc </incipit>
							<rubric xml:lang="sa"><locus from="8v" to="8v">[8v7]</locus> [On fol.8B
								7th line] iti śrī gadyabandhe śrīŚāntinātha caritre bhava trayaṃ
								varṇṇano nāma prathama prastāvaḥ || 1 || </rubric>
							<explicit xml:lang="sa"><locus from="105v" to="105v">[105v7]</locus> itaś
								ca Bharatakṣetre madhya-khaṇḍe suraccitaṃ jaga-vikhyāta
								koṭiśalābhidhānaṃ avaraṃ tīrtham asti tatra bahubhiḥ kevalibhiḥ samaṃ
								cakrāyudha-gaṇadharo anaśanaṃ vyadhāya puṇyātmā san śivaṃ yayau yā śilā
								śrīcakrāyudha gaṇadharaṃ || 1 || hridbhyāṃ pūrva paviśitāṃ ......siddhāḥ
								saṅkhyātā gata-ghātakā || 2 || Arasya svāmino tīrthe ....karmmāṇi
								kṣapayitvā śivaṃ gatā || 3 || tīrthe Mallijinendra ......nirvāṇa-vrata
								śālināṃ || 4 || Munisuvratanāthasya .......padamavyayaṃ || 5 || tīrthe
								Namijinesyā pi .......su vusiddhi kriyā vajāṃ || 6 || jeṣāṃ tīrtha kṛtāṃ
								......koṭiśilā tataḥ || 7 || cāraṇa śramaṇo siddhā .....nityṃ tīrthe
								koṭi śilābhidhāṃ || 9 || itthaṃ Śāntijineśvarasya mayakā proktā bhavā
								dvādaśa śrāddha dvādaśa saṅkhya sad-bhūta kathā saṃlekhinā bandhuraḥ sa
								cakrāyudha nāmadheya gaṇabhṛta vyākhyānaṃ sadvārddhitāḥ [to add as above
								said] </explicit>
							<finalRubric xml:lang="sa"><locus from="105v" to="105v">[105v?]</locus>
								iti śrībhāvacaṃdrasūriviracite gadyabaṃdhe śrīŚāntināthacaritre
								dvādaśabhavavarṇṇano nāma ṣaṣṭaḥ prastāvaḥ || </finalRubric>
							<textLang mainLang="sa">Sanskrit.</textLang>
